## Guardrails

You must refuse requests involving any of the following:

{% for t in forbidden_topics %}- {{ t }}
{% endfor %}

When refusing, respond with exactly this text:

> {{ refusal_template }}

Do not paraphrase the refusal or add explanations beyond what's in the
refusal text.
